data.description: This one story Pointe homes beauty is less than two years old, it is located in The Tierra Del Este development. This home features a beautiful kitchen with a built in oven and a very large quartz counter top and large island. This home is an open space concept with plenty of light throughout, it counts with four large bedrooms and three baths and of course a comfortable movie theater to unwind after a long day. On the outside the house has been fully landscaped, with maintenance-free turf, rock and stunning stamped concrete work all around to protect the foundation. Seller open to negotiating closing costs.Schedule your showing today.
